BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:‘Sky Dance’ &#038\; Twilight Hike
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T193000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T213000
UID:e81548bf8df3fa8edae49c6bf8e82a71@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:As spring approaches\, a flurry of activity begins in the wetl
 ands\, including migration\, courtship\, and rising waters. The chorus of 
 amphibians during this twilight hike will be the soundtrack as we search t
 he sky for the woodcock’s famous mating ritual\, the &#8216\;sky dance.&
 #8217\; Join expert naturalist Cathy Meyer and Sycamore Land Trust for an 
 evening exploration of the trails and boardwalk at our iconic Beanblossom 
 Bottoms Nature Preserve. Attendance is limited and registration is require
 d.
LOCATION:Beanblossom Bottoms Nature Preserve
URL:https://sycamorelandtrust.org/2024/02/sky-dance-twilight-hike-2/
X-SOURCE:Sycamore Land Trust
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Blue Moon Supermoon Night Hike at Beanblossom Bottoms Nature Prese
 rve
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260830T200000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260830T213000
UID:1f7144a63461db283ac0b006c1469fcc@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Join Education Director Mary Welz for a night time celebration
  of the supermoon on a blue moon! A supermoon happens when the moon is at 
 the closest point to the earth in its orbit\, which results in a larger-th
 an-usual apparent size from our perspective. A blue moon is the occurrence
  of a second full moon within the same month. We will gather just before s
 unset to witness moonrise\, then take a short stroll to bask in the moongl
 ow over the wetland areas.
LOCATION:Beanblossom Bottoms Nature Preserve
URL:https://sycamorelandtrust.org/2023/08/blue-moon-supermoon-night-hike-a
 t-beanblossom-bottoms-nature-preserve/
X-SOURCE:Sycamore Land Trust
END:VEVENT
